 henna.&#160\;Come and learn&#160\;the basic designs and application techn
 iques of&#160\;Henna&#160\;or&#160\;Mehendi\, which&#160\;is&#160\;used t
 o create temporary tattoos. Please feel free to bring your friends to lea
 rn more about Desi culture and the significance of&#160\;Mehendi&#160\;in
  the Indian culture! If you come with a group of more than 7 members\, pl
 ease email&#160\;acc@iu.edu&#160\;in advance so we can prepare the henna 
 materials.&#160\;&#160\;&#160\;  &#160\;For more information\, view this 
 event in BeInvolved (https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11988305).
