SUMMARY:Mahjong Monday
DESCRIPTION:At the ACC\, we offer a casual and informal mahjong experienc
 e\, perfect for those looking to learn the game\, take a break from the d
 igital world\, and most importantly\, meet new friends in person. You do 
 not need to be an expert to join usâ€”just bring your enthusiasm and a wi
 llingness to learn!All Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, 
