 At the ACC\, we offer a casual and informal mahjong experience\, perfect 
 for those looking to learn the game\, take a break from the digital world
 \, and most importantly\, meet new friends in person. You do not need to 
 be an expert to join usâ€”just bring your enthusiasm and a willingness to
  learn!</span></p><br /><p><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">All I
 ndiana University events\, groups\, activities\, educational\, cultural\,
  and historical observances welcome all members of the Indiana University
  community.</span></p><br /><strong>For more information\, <a href="https
 ://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11988041">view this event in BeInvolved</
