SUMMARY:Inherited / Becoming: AAPI Creative Lineage Mixer
DESCRIPTION:The Eskenazi School of Art\, Architecture + Design\, in colla
 boration with the Art Therapy Program at the Sidney and Lois Eskenazi Mus
 eum of Art\, invites you to a creative gathering of collage-making and co
 nversation in celebration of Asian American Pacific Islander (AAPI) Herit
 age Month. Using simple collage materials\, participants will respond to 
 the prompt"Who/What/Where/Why do you come from?"\,reflecting on backgroun
 d\, culture\, memory\, and legacy. Throughmaking andsmall-group dialogue\
 , attendees can share the stories and imagery that shape their experience
 s while exploring both shared and unique cultural connections. No artisti
 c experience is necessary. Open to all. Light refreshments will be provid
 ed.
